title: Pro-LifT F-2315PE Grey Hydraulic Trolley Jack Car Lift with Blow Molded Case-3000 LBS Capacity, 12 Inch
description: Pro lift F-2315PE hydraulic trolley jack has the 3000 lbs. capacity. It gives you the ability to lift from 5.25" to 12". it is built with All welded steel frame construction and rust-resistant. Large steel casters and swivel casters provide easy maneuverability.
